{
  "stem": "1537.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now the American Army came on May 5, 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what happened when I was laying there already, I was still, you know, I was thinking of course, I was no-- I don't know, I didn't care-- die.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't matter any more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was happy a little bit that, you know, we are liberated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I say what's going to be with me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I going to die here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because before the SS run away, the bulldozers dig all those big graves, the mass graves to push everybody in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so anyway the Americans arrive, and I stay there for the night, yeah, in a jeep with American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I managed to get into the forest, because the boys who left on the highway-- because the war was still going on-- told them that there is a camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they managed to get in with a jeep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they are telling us we have to get out to the road, to the main road, that the Americans should see us, to take us to hospitals, or to-- they made refugee camps right away.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But here, you see, you can all die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cannot-- they will not find you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, you know, we spoke a little bit Yiddish, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I says, I cannot go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, I'm too weak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I say, you have to get out there on the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I stay there for the night, you know, laying between the dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And next morning, I see it's getting less and less.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody, almost everybody is dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only a few people move a little bit then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm the only, practically the only one who is still there alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
